OL,3,CMum on trial for murder: What it was
OL,4,Clike in the courtroom
OL,6,FWe were to hear of how a mother
OL,7,Fdeliberately burned her three-year-old
OL,8,Fson in a bath of scalding-hot water,
OL,9,Fleaving the wounds effectively
OL,10,Funtreated for 18 days; how a mother
OL,11,Fbeat her son with a cane because the
OL,12,Fbible tells her that she should
OL,13,Fchastise her child; how a mother
OL,14,Fpicked up her son and shook him so
OL,15,Fviolently that it killed him.
