OL,3,CMum on trial for murder: What it was
OL,4,Clike in the courtroom
OL,6,FAs the prosecution presented its case,
OL,7,Fthe court's sitting times were
OL,8,Farranged around a schedule that
OL,9,Fallowed Robinson to express milk for
OL,10,Fher baby son. He was born last year
OL,11,Fafter she became pregnant using a
OL,12,Fsperm donor shortly before murdering
OL,13,FDwelaniyah.
OL,15,FOn 13 March she took the stand to give
OL,16,Fevidence in her defence. As she faced
OL,17,Fthe jury, she sat on a high stool in
OL,18,Fthe witness box, wearing a black shrug
OL,19,Fand a grey jumper dress.
