OL,3,CMum on trial for murder: What it was
OL,4,Clike in the courtroom
OL,6,F"There is nothing that says 'she
OL,7,Fdeliberately did this'. Nothing that
OL,8,Fsays 'this is her handprints'. Nothing
OL,9,Fthat ties me directly to killing
OL,10,Fanybody."
OL,12,FThe jury, though, disagreed.
OL,14,FAfter the forewoman delivered the
OL,15,Fverdict, several of the jurors once
OL,16,Fagain became visibly upset.
