OL,7,Fbeen the case from the moment police
OL,8,Ffirst visited her house and throughout
OL,9,Fthe trial, showed no emotion as she
OL,10,Fwas taken away to begin what the judge
OL,11,Fsaid will inevitably be a life
OL,12,Fsentence.
